-- 2013-06-26T16:34:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-26/val-ackerman-is-hired-as-commissioner-of-big-east-conference.html
Val Ackerman was hired as
commissioner of the revised Big East conference, the New York-based college sports league announced.  Ackerman was the first head of the Women’s  National
Basketball Association  and brings a long history of
administration in the sport to a league that’s turning its focus
back to basketball.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Larry Siddons at 
 lsiddons@bloomberg.net  